              conditions with lower humidity and stable temperatures, making it ideal for exterior projects. 
              Winter brings occasional freezes that can affect exterior work, but interior projects can 
              continue year-round. We plan all projects around these weather patterns to ensure optimal 
              results and lasting finishes that can withstand Fairhope's unique climate challenges.
